{"tid":2209120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實宜家報消委會係咪已經無用？","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T20:37:42.000Z","uid":366484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef75764d32e60e692ded3de6de70343f68606265","tid":2209120,"uid":366484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"部電腦琴日收到就已經壞左，個芒上面有pat黑色野，底部仲跳曬格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去門市想claim保養，結果佢話見到個芒有撞擊痕跡所以唔包，但我無搞過佢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話我proof唔到我無撞過個芒，我又話佢proof唔到佢唔係一開始就腥爛機比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我收到部機第一日就壞左，收到嘅第二日早上急急忙忙去左你地門市整，點都唔似係果d自己玩下玩下整爛果類柒頭啦，個on9 staff仲好死到同我講「Er小姐你宜家部野已經賣左比你，所以已經唔係我地公司property，所以有問題都唔應該搵我地負責」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂大佬我用bts買所以一定係佢寄上門，無得自己去門市取貨，你以為我想？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算有問題都要自己嚮屋企拆左先知，又無理由叫個順豐仔企嚮門口等你慢慢左望右望部機，通常係個包裹無穿無爛就算，點知就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇個樣果邊似係溝通唔到，報消委會會唔會有用？求各位Ching教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637880614c1a50fd06c26d6f73781692e45091af","tid":2209120,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"8257fe567260016aa1ecccc637a4ae6ccfbd8caa","tid":2209120,"uid":366484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"有無人可以教下我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d394cdc197965b55aa22d0697c6fef1e566c3175","tid":2209120,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8257fe567260016aa1ecccc637a4ae6ccf